    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  Using a set of programs for analyzing the primary structure of amyloidogenic proteins, we analyzed the primary structure of the of the COVID-19 NSP7 protein. Peptides containing potential amyloidogenic determinants in the primary structure have been synthesized and shown to be capable of forming amyloid-like fibrils\n                  <jats:italic>in vitro</jats:italic>\n                  . In the future, this peptide can be used as a basis for creating antiviral agents that act directly on the spatial structure of the NSP7 subunit of the COVID-19 polymerase.\n                </jats:p>",
